<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Complaint Notification - Bighil Platform</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #198754;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        max-width: 150px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: white;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .alert-icon {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .alert-icon::before {
        content: "!";
        display: inline-block;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background-color: #198754;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 50%;
        line-height: 60px;
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .notification {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .notification h2 {
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .notification p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .complaint-details {
        background-color: #f8fffe;
        border: 1px solid #198754;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .complaint-details h3 {
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .complaint-id {
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
        background-color: white;
        padding: 12px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        border: 2px solid #198754;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .complaint-info {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: white;
        padding: 12px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .complaint-info:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .complaint-info .label {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .complaint-info .value {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .next-steps {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #198754;
      }

      .next-steps h3 {
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .next-steps ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .next-steps li {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding-left: 20px;
        position: relative;
      }

      .next-steps li::before {
        content: "â€¢";
        color: #198754;
        font-weight: bold;
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
      }

      .important-notice {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        border: 1px solid #198754;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .important-notice h3 {
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .important-notice p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .cta-button {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .cta-button a {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #198754;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        margin: 0 10px 10px 0;
      }

      .cta-button a:hover {
        background-color: #146c43;
      }

      .cta-button a.secondary {
        background-color: white;
        color: #198754;
        border: 2px solid #198754;
      }

      .cta-button a.secondary:hover {
        background-color: #f8fffe;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .footer p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #198754;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      /* Mobile Responsive */
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .email-container {
          margin: 0 10px;
          border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 20px 15px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .notification h2 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .complaint-details,
        .next-steps,
        .important-notice {
          padding: 15px;
        }

        .complaint-info {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          padding: 10px;
        }

        .complaint-info .label {
          margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
          padding: 15px 20px;
        }

        .cta-button a {
          display: block;
          margin: 10px 0;
          padding: 12px 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .notification h2 {
          font-size: 18px;
        }

        .complaint-id {
          font-size: 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= logoPath %>" alt="Bighil Platform Logo" class="logo" />
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="alert-icon"></div>

        <div class="notification">
          <h2>Complaint Filed Against Your Organization</h2>
          <p>Dear <%= role %>,</p>
          <p>
            We are writing to inform you that a complaint has been filed against
            your organization through the Bighil Platform. This notification is
            part of our transparent complaint management process.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="complaint-details">
          <h3>Complaint Reference Details:</h3>
          <div class="complaint-id"><%= complaintId %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-button">
          <a href="<%= redirectLink %>">View Complaint Details</a>
        </div>

        <div
          style="
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
          "
        >
          <p><strong>Need Assistance?</strong></p>
          <p>
            Our support team is available to guide you through this process and
            answer any questions you may have.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are committed to ensuring a fair and efficient resolution for all
            parties involved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          <strong>Bighil Platform - Transparent Complaint Management</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          For immediate assistance, visit our
          <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>">Support Center</a> or contact our
          resolution team.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #999">
          This is an automated notification. Please use the dashboard to
          communicate regarding this complaint.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
